Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.57,0:00:06.93,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你到底是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.19,0:00:09.17,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}莫名其妙地就倒下了  吓了我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.51,0:00:12.15,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}突然眼前一黑  脚一软…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.27,0:00:13.99,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}抱歉  让你担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.90,0:00:16.46,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}轻度贫血吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.56,0:00:18.12,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}怎么办  去医院吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.26,0:00:19.33,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不  没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.45,0:00:21.31,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我想休息一下就会好的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.85,0:00:24.58,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}补习已经开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.22,0:00:28.05,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}一天不去也没什么大的影响吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.30,0:00:29.24,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}今天就休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.33,0:00:29.80,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.33,0:00:31.97,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}往人不去打工吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.04,0:00:33.17,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}今天不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.51,0:00:40.61,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}与往人一起去了学校
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.96,0:00:42.73,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}与往人一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.90,0:00:46.16,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}知了撞进了往人的早饭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.40,0:00:48.47,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}与往人一起去了车站
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.70,0:00:50.62,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}与往人一起去了神社
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.46,0:00:54.20,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不可以看人家的日记
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.00,0:00:57.16,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你就不会写点别的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.70,0:01:00.10,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}呵呵  我觉得写得满好的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.52,0:01:04.27,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}听好  说实话你没有写日记的天赋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.58,0:01:07.89,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}所以今后不要总写做过的事  要写想要做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.00,0:01:10.05,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}可是  那样就不是日记
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.10,0:01:11.39,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不  是日记
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.67,0:01:14.42,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}因为我会实现你写的所有的愿望的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.25,0:01:18.34,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好想去海边啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.92,0:01:20.10,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}与往人一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.07,0:01:23.80,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}还没和你一起到过沙滩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.36,0:01:27.79,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}在那里挖沙子啦  捡漂亮的贝壳啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.37,0:01:31.68,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我说  你不是每天都能看到海么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.51,0:01:33.26,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嘎哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.82,0:01:34.45,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好疼～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.89,0:01:35.70,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.17,0:01:40.04,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}陪你去海边
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.37,0:01:42.93,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.81,0:03:26.76,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那孩子说想要去海边
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.40,0:03:30.01,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}但我却没能带她去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.73,0:03:41.57,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}观铃病倒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.92,0:03:44.67,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是啊  一整天了都没好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.99,0:03:46.12,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}正在房间里休息呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.27,0:03:47.53,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你去看看她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.26,0:03:52.38,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}让她看到我这幅醉样  病情就变得更糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.48,0:03:54.35,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}先不管她  看我买了寿司
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.50,0:03:56.43,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}咱们来高兴高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.34,0:04:03.68,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊…  你刚才的举动极大地伤害了我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.98,0:04:06.20,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你为什么要收养观铃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.53,0:04:07.09,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.48,0:04:09.81,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你为什么收养了观铃！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.23,0:04:12.91,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}什么嘛  原来她对你讲了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.10,0:04:17.92,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不是收养  是别人硬塞给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.43,0:04:20.70,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}虽然我说了不愿意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.76,0:04:23.63,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}正因如此  她才无法向你撒娇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.81,0:04:26.82,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}有点负责感好不好！  你可是她唯一的亲人！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.41,0:04:30.56,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那孩子要和谁变得亲近时就会发作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.64,0:04:33.80,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我和那孩子之间保持着一定的距离
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.36,0:04:36.11,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}因此才能生活在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.93,0:04:38.36,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}根本不像一对母女是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.76,0:04:41.36,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我自己也不是她真正的母亲  所以什么也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.15,0:04:45.09,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}真难吃  买错东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.94,0:04:55.57,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}女孩在做梦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.23,0:04:58.27,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}最初是个天空的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.84,0:05:01.20,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}梦渐渐地追溯着过去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.25,0:05:05.22,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就是那个梦在侵蚀着女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.20,0:05:08.70,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}渐渐地  她会开始感觉到本不该有的痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.32,0:05:12.35,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不久  女孩将会忘记一切
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.18,0:05:17.47,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}甚至连自己最亲近的人都忘掉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.68,0:05:20.97,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}然后在做完最后一场梦的早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.54,0:05:23.20,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}女孩会死去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.67,0:05:26.56,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那孩子一直孤零零的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.59,0:05:30.96,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}因为两个人的心靠近的话  两个人都会病倒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.49,0:05:32.96,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}两个人都无法得救
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.90,0:05:35.34,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}所以那个女孩说了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.99,0:05:37.60,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}「离开我…」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.14,0:05:41.60,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}她是个善良并且坚强的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.04,0:05:43.96,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}也正因此我才能活了下来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.01,0:05:46.44,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}但是  那孩子却…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.58,0:05:51.60,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}在这片天空中  有一个拥有一双翅膀的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.43,0:05:56.06,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}她总是孤零零的一个人  长不大就消逝了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.64,0:05:58.86,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}一个人重复着那个悲伤的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.02,0:06:05.17,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}去旅行！？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.43,0:06:06.96,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}对  一个人悠然地去旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.04,0:06:08.23,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}温泉之旅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.10,0:06:10.98,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你到底在想什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.10,0:06:13.24,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}她…  观铃怎么办！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.54,0:06:14.85,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.94,0:06:18.27,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}别太接近她的话  也就不会发作了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.47,0:06:20.18,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.97,0:06:22.74,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}观铃正在做着一个梦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.05,0:06:25.64,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就是那个梦把观铃弄成这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.99,0:06:26.54,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.96,0:06:29.69,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我想起了妈妈说过的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.28,0:06:33.41,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我妈妈以前也遇到过这种病状的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.86,0:06:35.53,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}再过不久  观铃会忘记一切
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.63,0:06:37.33,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}忘记我  也忘记你…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.96,0:06:40.46,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}然后在做完最后一场梦的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.60,0:06:42.63,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}观铃  可能会死去…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.66,0:06:48.24,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我说  开玩笑也得分轻重
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.37,0:06:50.64,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}这不是玩笑  观铃她…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.66,0:06:51.29,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}躲开
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.03,0:06:52.51,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.88,0:06:57.48,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我进来了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.56,0:07:01.06,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}怎么  醒着呢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.46,0:07:03.94,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯  刚醒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.60,0:07:06.57,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我听到了妈妈的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.85,0:07:09.53,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊  说是出去一段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.88,0:07:10.87,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.67,0:07:16.44,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我非常喜欢妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.66,0:07:22.76,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}去海边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.79,0:07:32.02,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}慢慢走  不用勉强
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.38,0:07:32.89,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.80,0:07:36.17,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊  是乌鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.46,0:07:41.05,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}观铃！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.48,0:07:43.90,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}喂  没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.01,0:07:44.49,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.80,0:07:46.76,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.41,0:07:49.94,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}V～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.22,0:07:53.35,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}明明每天都走过这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.73,0:07:56.19,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}海有这么遥远吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.42,0:08:02.00,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.28,0:08:07.00,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.36,0:08:11.89,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我又…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.86,0:08:14.14,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}又要发作吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.42,0:08:15.23,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.20,0:08:19.41,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}一会儿就会好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.18,0:08:22.98,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}海…  明天再去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.70,0:08:31.46,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}平静下来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.21,0:08:32.67,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.91,0:08:35.34,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}呐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.60,0:08:38.41,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}昨晚我又做梦了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.78,0:08:40.81,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}这回是个快乐的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.27,0:08:43.59,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}虽然是黑夜但天空很亮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.27,0:08:46.46,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我想那一定是节日祭奠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.07,0:08:49.10,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我就那样在远处眺望着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.77,0:08:50.35,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.15,0:08:52.14,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}往人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.47,0:08:53.07,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.23,0:08:56.27,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}往人正在寻找的那个人和我的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.51,0:08:58.09,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是相互联系的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.39,0:09:00.83,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}谁知道呢  应该不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.75,0:09:06.74,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我思考了很多后得出一个结论
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.82,0:09:07.98,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}愿意听我说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.62,0:09:11.65,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我的梦代表着另外的那个我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.14,0:09:15.18,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}现在  那个孩子正在痛苦着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.86,0:09:18.13,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我要努力地做梦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.93,0:09:22.09,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}因为多做些梦  也许就会明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.93,0:09:26.94,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}这样  也许就能够帮助那个孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.21,0:09:32.75,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}往人  我开始做这个梦并不是偶然的对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.25,0:09:36.29,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我认为今年的夏天是不同寻常的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.63,0:09:38.94,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我想努力去交朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.48,0:09:42.52,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}于是便遇到了往人  然后开始做梦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.94,0:09:45.15,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}这一切一定都是相互联系的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.12,0:09:48.17,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}所以  我想努力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.55,0:09:51.27,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}想把这个夏天作为自己最美的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.47,0:09:53.57,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}因为这是和往人相遇的夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.75,0:09:58.36,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.56,0:10:01.46,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.69,0:10:03.37,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我感觉舒服多了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.40,0:10:08.98,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哇！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.70,0:10:10.29,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}观铃！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.81,0:10:13.95,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哎？  这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.84,0:10:16.39,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}脚无法动了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.98,0:10:30.29,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}还是把圣叫来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.77,0:10:32.33,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}要不去大的医院
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.09,0:10:36.72,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不  医生肯定是治不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.27,0:10:39.79,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}其实往人也是知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.60,0:10:44.10,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就是我做的那个梦把我弄成这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.35,0:10:45.13,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}这…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.73,0:10:47.46,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}昨天晚上我又做梦了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.90,0:10:49.05,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是一个旅途的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.51,0:10:50.10,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}旅途？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.52,0:10:52.05,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}寻找什么东西的旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.55,0:10:55.66,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我在森林中走了好多天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.21,0:10:58.12,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}虽然很累  但我努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.59,0:11:01.02,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}因为有喜欢的人陪在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.12,0:11:02.21,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}喜欢的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.60,0:11:03.81,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我自己明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.97,0:11:07.61,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我每做一次梦  就会变得衰弱一些
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.97,0:11:10.69,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}最终一定会像天空中的少女那样…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.71,0:11:12.33,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}别说傻话！  怎么可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.61,0:11:14.80,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}呵呵  往人生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.27,0:11:18.02,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不要去想什么另外的那个你的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.29,0:11:19.69,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}先把病养好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.60,0:11:22.89,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯  观铃是坚强的孩子！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.11,0:11:49.89,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}往人！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.04,0:11:51.75,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}往人！  往人！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.63,0:11:54.56,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.25,0:11:56.55,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}没事…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.88,0:11:59.72,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}没事的话就不会那副表情了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.46,0:12:02.34,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我原本就是这副表情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.51,0:12:03.99,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}观铃  回床上去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.10,0:12:05.88,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我不能不管往人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.07,0:12:09.04,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我说了没事了  不要太让我操心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.71,0:12:10.24,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.36,0:12:22.03,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}这痕迹是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.83,0:12:28.82,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好疼！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.34,0:12:30.75,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}观铃  振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.53,0:12:35.27,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}观铃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.50,0:12:45.43,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}没关系的  一会就好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.82,0:12:47.05,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}陪着我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.10,0:12:48.73,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}可是我在你身边的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.14,0:12:51.62,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}没关系  陪着我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.69,0:12:59.36,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}为什么大家只把我留下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.61,0:13:05.87,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}感觉怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.53,0:13:07.50,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}现在没事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.60,0:13:08.70,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}往人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.98,0:13:10.30,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我什么事都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.87,0:13:12.89,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}怎么办  还是叫圣来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.34,0:13:14.01,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}或是叫佳乃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.21,0:13:16.50,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}美风已经离开小镇了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.60,0:13:17.66,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}要不叫个同学来…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.75,0:13:20.65,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不用了  我不想给别人添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.90,0:13:23.71,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}别说瞎话  你很想交朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.81,0:13:24.94,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不喜欢一个人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.81,0:13:27.24,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}往人在就好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.46,0:13:30.27,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}有往人陪着我  其他的什么都不要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.91,0:13:31.90,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}会不会给你添麻烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.33,0:13:32.95,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}怎么会！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.71,0:13:38.31,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好想和往人一起去海边啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.45,0:13:39.90,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}在沙滩上玩耍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.19,0:13:43.06,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}追逐跑啦  打水仗啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.27,0:13:45.73,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}最后大家挥手道别
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.86,0:13:48.31,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不过现在我先忍着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.69,0:13:52.32,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}这样到时候真去的时候会更高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.74,0:13:54.32,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}观铃加油～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.28,0:13:56.04,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.07,0:13:57.69,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}观铃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.78,0:13:58.34,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.59,0:14:00.21,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我觉得差不多该离开了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.99,0:14:08.06,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}再这样下去的话  我俩都会病倒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.68,0:14:11.41,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}所以我决定逃离这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.86,0:14:15.52,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}离开这个小镇  去一个再也不会见到你的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.81,0:14:16.64,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}一个人…？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.08,0:14:17.65,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.32,0:14:21.16,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我们靠得太近了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.05,0:14:26.82,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那就…  没办法了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.46,0:14:28.82,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}没办法了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.78,0:14:33.27,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我就说嘛  一直一个人玩的话就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.08,0:14:34.83,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}也许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.76,0:14:39.43,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}这个暑假过的很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.81,0:14:41.97,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}和往人一起度过的这个暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.10,0:14:44.93,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.37,0:14:46.06,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.40,0:14:46.88,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.77,0:14:51.38,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}已经没车了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.78,0:14:53.90,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}往人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.51,0:14:59.38,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那个…  今早的梦…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.64,0:15:01.93,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我一个人被孤零零地关了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.03,0:15:03.05,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}很寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.27,0:15:07.42,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}一直在等着谁来带我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.66,0:15:11.81,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我…我也想和往人一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.12,0:15:14.31,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不能带我一起去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.95,0:15:17.66,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我不是想离开这个家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.99,0:15:20.03,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是必须要离开你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.88,0:15:24.11,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}只要我不在了  你的病应该可以治好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.65,0:15:28.00,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}所以  我是无法陪在你身边的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.05,0:15:28.88,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.03,0:15:30.36,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.62,0:15:33.37,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}抱歉  又说了傻话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.82,0:15:34.32,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}没什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.80,0:15:39.93,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那再见了…  保重身体
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.14,0:15:41.75,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你也要加油
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.08,0:15:43.65,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}一个人也要加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.99,0:15:45.85,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯  一个人也要加油
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.15,0:15:47.50,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我是坚强的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.82,0:15:49.80,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好  再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.23,0:15:57.98,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}观铃…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.41,0:16:25.86,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}往人现在在想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.08,0:16:28.56,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}有没有想着要让看的人欢笑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.07,0:16:30.78,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不这样的话是无法操动人偶的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.20,0:16:33.16,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不能只想着要让人偶动起来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.33,0:16:36.70,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}要想着为什么要让人偶动起来  这样人偶就会动了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.98,0:16:44.08,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}做的不错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.33,0:16:50.24,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那孩子说想去海边
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.97,0:16:53.49,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}但我却没能带她去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.19,0:16:57.52,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}往人  这回你一定要救她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.48,0:17:00.18,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}在这个人偶里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.51,0:17:03.06,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}聚集着未能实现的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.68,0:17:08.57,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我的母亲  祖母等在身体衰弱前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.74,0:17:11.22,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}都把自己的力量封印在了这个人偶里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.92,0:17:15.03,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}为了有一天有个人可以实现这个愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.04,0:17:19.64,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}所以  我也会变成愿望中的一个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.40,0:17:22.93,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}如何使用这个人偶是你的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.51,0:17:26.89,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就算忘记天空中那个女孩也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.26,0:17:29.29,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}但是往人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.33,0:17:33.52,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}在某个小镇上  你一定会和那个女孩相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.67,0:17:37.46,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}如果你无论如何都想救那个女孩的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.90,0:17:40.01,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就心念这个人偶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.83,0:17:43.58,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}因为我会和你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.62,0:17:48.93,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}心念这个人偶…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.54,0:17:54.00,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}这个大哥哥一直怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.81,0:17:58.37,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}天热中暑了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.88,0:18:03.98,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}放开我！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.49,0:18:07.82,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}拜托了  帮帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.95,0:18:12.07,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}看这个  告诉我如何做才能变的有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.14,0:18:14.57,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}如何做才能让别人欢笑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.83,0:18:16.16,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊  好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.20,0:18:17.33,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.48,0:18:19.88,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不过没什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.66,0:18:25.04,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}别光是走  让它再表演些其他的如何
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.84,0:18:27.93,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}比如装成说话的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.03,0:18:31.50,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}表演段舞蹈如何
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.82,0:18:33.11,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}舞…舞蹈…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.20,0:18:36.91,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}要更用心些才行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.77,0:18:57.21,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}刚才的表演非常有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.28,0:18:59.27,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}既有趣  又可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.50,0:19:00.04,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.15,0:19:02.29,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}谢谢啦  一直陪着我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.10,0:19:05.27,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那就加油吧  大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.46,0:19:06.25,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}再见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.52,0:19:25.44,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}观铃  我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.92,0:19:28.22,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哪里都不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.72,0:19:31.35,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}陪在你身边  让你一直欢笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.10,0:19:33.16,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}往人…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.50,0:19:34.78,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我找到窍门了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.93,0:19:36.68,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}这回的表演一定很有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.88,0:19:38.44,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}所以你要仔细看哟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.85,0:19:43.42,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}观铃！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.89,0:19:47.75,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}观铃！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.04,0:19:50.07,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你看啊！ 你笑啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.34,0:19:59.28,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}为什么我一直都没注意到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.91,0:20:01.36,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}陪在你的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.75,0:20:05.52,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}看着你的笑容就是我要追求的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.78,0:20:08.07,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那就是我要追求的幸福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.02,0:20:10.17,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我哪里都不会去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.03,0:20:12.37,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}在我的身边欢笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.08,0:20:15.17,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}呐…  观铃…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.84,0:20:22.60,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}往人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.08,0:20:24.75,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你现在一定要想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.08,0:20:26.62,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}自己必须做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.27,0:20:31.37,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我… 我想陪在观铃身边
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.94,0:20:34.84,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}可以的话  想从与她相遇的时候起重新来过
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.54,0:20:36.88,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}这回一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.46,0:20:39.34,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}永远陪在观铃身边…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.76,0:20:49.02,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.48,0:20:51.86,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}本以为无法再起来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.03,0:20:53.79,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}往人…？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.55,0:20:55.84,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你去哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.35,0:20:58.31,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你回来看我了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.93,0:21:02.00,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你看  我又恢复健康了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.56,0:21:04.39,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我还可以加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.59,0:21:06.14,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}呐…  往人…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.66,0:21:24.66,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好疼──
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.55,0:21:28.52,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你为何在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.38,0:21:31.67,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}有空说话的话赶快给我起来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.21,0:21:34.33,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}没见过你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.80,0:21:38.07,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}正八位下左卫门大志 柳也
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.83,0:21:41.43,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你是从哪里掉下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.79,0:21:43.70,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你不知道我的名字吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.95,0:21:46.10,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不知道  咱们才刚刚见面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.18,0:21:48.22,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.65,0:21:50.86,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}竟然还有人不知道我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.64,0:21:52.40,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神奈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.79,0:21:54.34,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那可真是巧了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.51,0:21:57.41,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我奉命要保护的翼人的名字也是神奈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.53,0:21:59.51,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哦～　真的是很巧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.63,0:22:03.81,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就是说嘛  哈哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.76,0:22:06.78,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}蠢材！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.78,0:23:46.52,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}说到翼人  是神的使者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.02,0:23:50.76,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}当遇到饥荒和疫病时  祈祷神的力量来保护大家
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.92,0:23:53.64,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是可以直接和神对话的人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.94,0:23:59.28,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}所谓家族  就是大家聚在一起生活
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.76,0:24:02.87,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好想见妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.68,0:24:07.02,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}没有比见不到母亲更残酷的事了
